---
import CenterContainer from "./centerContainer.astro";
---

<script>
  import AOS from "aos";
  import "aos/dist/aos.css";
  AOS.init({ duration: 1000 });
</script>

<div id="about-page"></div>
<main
  class="h-[unset] pt-24 relative sm:bg-cover bg-background"
  data-aos="fade-up"
>
  <CenterContainer class="w-full flex flex-col items-center md:flex px-4">
    <div
      class="text-center font-['PopinsSemiBold'] text-[28px] md:text-5xl leading-[120%] mb-3 md:mb-4"
    >
      About Tomo
    </div>
    <div
      class="text-center font-['PopinsNormal'] text-[rgba(18,18,18,0.75)] font-normal text-sm md:text-lg mb-4 md:mb-7"
    >
      Tomo is an all-in-one Web3 social wallet designed to bring the mass adoption of crypto. It allows users to log in effortlessly with their social accounts and supports multiple chains, with a particular emphasis on bringing Bitcoin into Ethereum L2, Solana and Cosmos ecosystems.
    </div>
    <div
        class="text-center font-['PopinsNormal'] text-[rgba(18,18,18,0.75)] font-normal text-sm md:text-lg mb-4 md:mb-7"
    >
      On Tomo, users can easily manage assets, send crypto to each other, chat, post content, make friends, and participate in token-based interest groups. They can also on-ramp fiat currency with a credit card, trade crypto assets, create Tomojis, and more. Designed to be a comprehensive power app, Tomo meets all your Web3 needs.
    </div>
    <img src="/images/about-img-1.svg" class="hidden md:flex mb-8" />
    <img src="/images/about-img-3.svg" class="md:hidden flex mb-8" />
    <img src="/images/about-img-2.svg" class="flex w-40 md:w-[unset]" />
  </CenterContainer>
</main>
